&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work remotely with customers sent directly to you, allowing you to collaborate with them virtually at times that work best for both parties.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide legal service to Rocket Lawyer members via paid engagements to deliver clearly defined legal services&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide legal information to customers via brief, written responses using our Ask a Legal Pro service.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Connect with customers by phone for 20-minute live consults requested and scheduled from the Rocket Lawyer platform.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
